title: Miha Golob
text:
Miha Golob (born 9 December 1980) is a Slovenian <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er.
He played for Ježica, <a href="NK%20Rudar%20Velenje">Rudar Velenje</a>, <a href="GNK%20Dinamo%20Zagreb">Dinamo Zagreb</a>, <a href="NK%20Maribor">Maribor</a>, <a href="AEL%20Limassol">AEL Limassol</a>, <a href="Aris%20Limassol">Aris Limassol</a>, SV Wildon, and <a href="Murfeld">Murfeld</a>.
